south africas 28 million blacks have no vote in national 
affairs parliament has chambers for asians and people of 
mixedrace but the constitution gives almost total power to the 
party that wins the most votes among the 5 million whites 
militant antiapartheid leaders committed to the concept of 
oneperson onevote have ignored heunis speech but mainstream 
white newspapers sunday joined city press in depicting it as a 
milestone 
