patronage system blasting incumbent mayor anthony cucci for 
running a spoils system that punished public employees who 
didnt support his 1985 election bid 
his attempts to persuade the court that a new breeze blew into 
city hall on july 1 1985 are unavailing us district 
judge harold a ackerman said he ruled that a police officer was 
illegally demoted for supporting thenmayor gerald mccann instead 
