assets dropped to a range of between 155000 and 435000 part of 
the difference can be attributed to the way speaker filled out his 
disclosure forms 
wright sold his fort worth home valued at between 100001 and 
250000 in august 1983 and purchased a more expensive home in 
mclean va which last year was appraised at more than 352000 
according to the wall street journal 
